Preheat oven to 375 degrees F (190 degrees C). Combine the pumpkin, SPLENDA(R), molasses, cinnamon, nutmeg, and salt in a bowl, mixing well. Add the egg whites and evaporated milk. Beat until smooth using a rotary or electric mixer. Stir in the mincemeat and pour into the unbaked pie shell. Bake at 375 degrees F (190 degrees C) for 40 minutes or until the filling is set. Cool slightly on a wire rack and serve warm.